  "text": "Influenza virus is well known for the worldwide pandemic and epidemic, and is a highly invasive virus that causes high level of morbidity. The first confirmed case of novel influenza A (H1N1) infection in Korea was registered on May 1, 2009 and 225 deaths had been reported by January 1, 2010 [CITATION_1] .",
